{"tid":1340884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要光復元朗嘅 全部同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:30:25.000Z","uid":13169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f11450b635e4900104ac439b6980704d231a82a","tid":1340884,"uid":13169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母睇到我堅嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩左幾年音樂<br />\n同大家介紹件好使好用嘅樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLCkdqJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLCkdqJ.png&h=b7943abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一棍在手 出街可以玩音樂又唔怕有人對你做啲咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">擋又得玩人體敲擊音樂</span></span><br />\n平個啲$30-40就有一對<br />\n有咩事斷左 換個對又得 反正咁平大家買多幾對去同人玩下敲擊樂都唔怕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好買啲垃圾棍啊！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家識做啦"},{"pid":"46680e1904bc325fe44a672ec3dd1e9f8e0e1636","tid":1340884,"uid":13169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:02.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講 我要見律師"},{"pid":"da4d7d62847a74530531529c1b75cc7cd328fd37","tid":1340884,"uid":13169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:13.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講 我要見律師 2"},{"pid":"20e33641f5cec44500dc3c32030ec7f3624e4397","tid":1340884,"uid":13169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:28.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講 我要見律師 3"},{"pid":"eacd28ff80c7bafe60aac9e1063b35c5c55f6bf2","tid":1340884,"uid":13169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講 我要見律師"},{"pid":"7accacba7859